                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": true
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "A CMake module currently exists for CxxTest and it is present in cmake-data Debian package, but the CxxTest framework is not in Debian repositories yet so I think that this tool can be useful.\n", 
